classes.description: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.

delay.description: Adds a transition delay, to allow a series of SpeedDialActions to be animated.

icon.description: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Fab.

slotProps.description: The props used for each slot inside.

slots.description: The components used for each slot inside.

sx.description: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles.

tooltipOpen.description: Make the tooltip always visible when the SpeedDial is open.

tooltipTitle.description: Label to display in the tooltip.

tooltipPlacementLeft.description: Styles applied to the root element if tooltipOpen={true} and `tooltipPlacement="left"``

tooltipPlacementRight.description: Styles applied to the root element if tooltipOpen={true} and `tooltipPlacement="right"``

slotDescriptions.root: The component that renders the root component.
slotDescriptions.tooltip: The component that renders the tooltip.
